what is AJAX 
AJAX stand for acychronous javascript XML used to send and recive data from client and server Acychronouly , different then regular HTTP request ,uses XMLHTTPrequest object carrier data xml,json,plain,text format


way of AJAX

regulalr AJAX request
fetch API
Axios library
Jquery library
node js http Module

why we use AJAX
No page  reload/refresh
better user expereince
saves netwok bandwidth
veryinteractive

how to it work

AJAX uses XMLHTTPrequesto object (also  called xhr object ) to achive this

data can be trasferred any format and protocol (NO always  https neccssairly)


